Title: S7 Ep. 282 Intern Whisperer Fan Favorites from 2023
Description:
We are so excited to share the top three winners from the Intern Whisperer 2023  annual competition of Intern Whisperer guests. We celebrate the top three most downloaded guests episodes based on guests sharing their episodes within their circle of influence. 

Who are these amazing guests:
1. Michelle Sanabria and Caleigh Hoyne with SMS Events Ep. 276
2. Wendy Austin with FIRST Robotics Ep. 240
3. Sam Sunmona with 8cast 
We also celebrate the top three guests that had the most views on the Employers 4 Change YouTube channel.  

1. Michelle Sanabria and Caleigh Hoyne with SMS Events Ep. 276
2. Caris Baker with Unity Technologies Ep.264
3. Roger Hunt with The Center for Innovative Ethics Ep. 268 and 
Honorable Mention for Bob Dixon with Arete Ep. 242
